{"tid":509421,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【蝗蟲天下】船灣淡水湖驚現逾千蝗蟲 專家疑有人亂放生損生態","createTime":"2017-12-25T09:50:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-25T09:50:08.000Z","uid":44358,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4c8296cf20e1930abeffb9feb3d48344fa5beb16","tid":509421,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T09:50:08.000Z","msg":"船灣淡水湖出現大量蝗蟲？市民李先生昨日在大埔新娘潭路船灣淡水湖集中區附近郊遊時，在草叢及地上發現大量疑似蝗蟲，數目估計逾千隻，在冬天仍跳來跳去，他感到不可思議，並憂若是有大量蝗蟲「來襲」，恐對郊野公園花草樹木造成災難，《蘋果》記者今日到場仍見到數百集疑似蝗蟲，但部分已斃命。有專家估計可能是有人拿蝗蟲來「放生」才造成此異象，並關注蝗蟲可能損害水塘區的生態，促當局正視。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171225/57625638\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171225%2F57625638&d=ZOOWPitwjGLyUMxvqtd0s8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=4901fdd0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171225%2F57625638&h=170a73cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171225/57625638</a>"}]}